# Interview Feature

The Perfect Interview application provides mock interview functionality as its core feature.

## Mock Interview Components

- [components/mock-interview](mdc:components/mock-interview): Contains all interview-related components
- Interview session management
- Question and answer handling
- Feedback and evaluation components

## AI Integration

- Uses AI models for generating interview questions and feedback
- Real-time transcription for spoken responses
- Response evaluation and scoring

## Interview Flow

1. User selects job role and interview type
2. System generates relevant interview questions
3. User provides answers (text or voice)
4. AI evaluates responses and provides feedback
5. Session results are saved for future reference

## Data Models

- Interview sessions
- Questions and responses
- User performance metrics
- Historical interview data
